    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been a fantastic car for me\u2014super reliable and still looks great on the road! It\u2019s in solid shape and drives like a dream, making it the perfect dependable daily driver. I\u2019ve really enjoyed my time with it and have kept it well-maintained, so it's all ready for its next adventure with you. Drop me a message if you\u2019d like to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
